EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
CAPE VERDE TO MADEIRA.
15 METER VESSEL MAYRA, WHITE HULL, OVERDUE
CAPE VERDE ISLANDS (15-06N 023-37W) TO
MADEIRA (32-39N 016-54W). VESSELS IN
VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC FALMOUTH,
PHONE: 44 132 631 7575, FAX: 44 132 631 5610,
E-MAIL: FALMOUTHCOASTGUARD@MCGA.GOV.UK.
